    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Employee
    Employee object keeps track of employee information and has severl get/set functions to manage said data.
    EmployeeController
    Controller for the EmployeeView part of the terminal
    EmployeeView
    a type of JPanel for viewing the Employee information stored in the database
    Inventory
    class for a type of item in the inventory system
    InventoryController
    ActionListener to control the InventoryView interface
    InventoryView
    JPanel to display the inventory information on screen
    LoginController
    Controller for the LoginScreen, is an ActionListener
    LoginScreen
    Login Screen JFrame
    MenuItem
    Class for an individual item on the menu
    MenuItemController
    controller to manage the items on the menu and their database entries
    MenuItemInventory
    Class for the inventory characteristics of an item
    MenuItemView
    JPanel for viewing the items on the menu
    Modifiers
    Modifiers JDialog for selecting the modifiers to the current item
    Order
    object for current order and its attributes
    OrderController
    controller for current order and the GUI that connects it
    OrderItem
    object for an item on an order
    OrderItem.IceLevel
    enum for IceLevel
    OrderItem.SugarLevel
    enum for sugar level
    OrderItem.Topping
    enum for selected topping
    ProductUsageController
    ActionListener to control product usage chart GUI
    ProductUsageView
    JPanel for the product usage chart
    ReportsView
    JPanel for the reports menu
    ReportViewMain
    ActionListener for ReportViewMain JFrame to connect GUI to actions
    SalesReportController
    ActionListener for salesReportView JFrame to connect GUI to actions
    SalesReportView
    JPanel for SalesReportView
    Terminal
    Terminal is a type of JFrame, it makes up the main window of the application
    XReportController
    XReport controller
    XReportView
    XReport JPanel for GUI rendering
    ZReportController
    ZReport controller
    ZReportView
    ZReport JPanel for GUI rendering
